cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.CE, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for disease prediction using bioinformatics tools and Artificial Neural Network (Backpropagation Network) for classification. This involves analyzing gene sequences and considering environmental factors. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), computational biology (cs.CE), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
